9,273]]\n! [[Washington gubernatorial election, 1960|50.3%]] || [[1960 Washington gubernatorial election|611,987]] \n|| [[Washington gubernatorial election, 1960|48.9%]] || [[1960 Washington gubernatorial election|594,122]]\n|-\n| '''1964'''\n! [[1964 United States presidential election in Washington (state)|62%]] || [[1964 United States presidential election in Washington (state)|779,881]] \n|| [[1964 United States presidential election in Washington (state)|37.4%]] || [[1964 United States presidential election in Washington (state)|470,366]] \n|| [[Washington gubernatorial election, 1964|43.9%]] || [[1964 Washington gubernatorial election|548,692]] \n! [[Washington gubernatorial election, 1964|55.8%]] || [[1964 Washington gubernatorial election|697,256]]\n|-\n| '''1968'''\n! [[1968 United States presidential election in Washington (state)|47.2%]] || [[1968 United States presidential election in Washington (state)|616,037]] \n|| [[1968 United States presidential election in Washington (state)|45.1%]] || [[1968 United States presidential election in Washington (state)|588,510]]\n|| [[Washington gubernatorial election, 1968|46.7%]] || [[1968 Washington gubernatorial election|881,994]] \n! [[Washington gubernatorial election, 1968|53.3%]] || [[1968 Washington gubernatorial election|1,006,993]]\n|-\n| '''1972'''\n|| [[1972 United States presidential election in Washington (state)|38.6%]] || [[1972 United States presidential election in Washington (state)|568,334]] \n! [[1972 United States presidential election in Washington (state)|56.9%]] || [[1972 United States presidential election in Washington (state)|837,135]]\n|| [[Washington gubernatorial election, 1972|42.8%]] || [[1972 Washington gubernatorial election|630,613]] \n! [[Washington gubernatorial election, 1972|50.8%]] || [[1972 Washington gubernatorial election|747,825]]\n|-\n| '''1976'''\n|| [[1976 United States presidential election in Washington (state)|46.1%]] || [[1976 United States presidential election in